Problem: 

1. Write a library providing an event producer/listener 

framework. Create an event class that the library user can subclass. Create an event producer class that the 

library user can use for his/her classes that can produce events. Create an event listener class that the library 

user can use for his/her classes to respond to the event occurrences.

2. Make it thread safe

3. Write a test program or caller of this library.
